            <paragraph>The timer will be dereferenced after its time elapses. To preserve the timer, you can keep a reference to it. See <reference internal="True" refuri="class_refcounted#class-refcounted"><inline classes="std std-ref">RefCounted</inline></reference>.</paragraph>
